Interface WTList

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.util.Collection, java.lang.Iterable, java.util.List, WTCollection

    public interface WTList
extends WTCollection, java.util.List
    A WTCollection that implements the java.util.List interface.

    Extendable: false
